    <title>Deleting entities from the entities column</title>
    <shortdesc>The CWRC-Writer templates comes with pre existing annotated entities as examples to
        new users. You can easily delete these entities, any entities that you don't want in you
        document, or those you have mistakenly added from the entities panel. </shortdesc>
